SUMMARY:Introduction to Dungeons & Dragons for Adults NEW (RESCHEDULED)
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to register on 
 the Adult School website\n\nHave you always wanted to learn how to play 
 this classic fantasy-based game? Do you have a young relative in your life 
 who loves D&D? Our seasoned dungeon master Jeremy Doyle will spend a half 
 hour cluing you into the basics of how to play and help you develop your 
 own character. Then you'll spend an hour participating in an exciting\, 
 imaginative campaign. On Monday\, February 9\, you'll get to use your new 
 character and new skills in another absorbing 1.5 session of play. All 
 materials\, dice\, board\, and character sheets included.
