SUMMARY:Teen Anime Club (ages 12 - 18)
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to the second edition of Montclair Public Library's 
 Teen Anime Club. We have a new format\, but the topic is still the same: 
 Anime!\n\nEach month\, we will be watching the first season (12 episodes) 
 of a series and gathering together to have a discussion\, do an activity\, 
 and enjoy snacks. We will not be watching the show together during club\, 
 so you must watch it on your own time before we meet.\n\nUnable to attend? 
 Don't worry! We will be posting about what the series that we will be 
 watching on the Teen Instagram as well as our Teen Discord! \n\nJanuary 7: 
 This month we will be explaining this new format\, handing out some 
 journaling supplies\, and selecting our first series to watch for our 
 February meeting. (Yes there will still be snacks to enjoy).\n\nFebruary 4: 
 Tokyo Revengers\n\nMarch 4: TBD\n\nApril 1: TBD\n\nMay 6: TBD\n\nJune 3: 
 TBD\n\nSign up for the Monthly Teen Newsletter\n
