SUMMARY:The Mediterranean Diet and Olive Oil Tasting
DESCRIPTION:This is a free Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nDid you miss out on this great free class last year because we 
 ran out of room? Well\, here's your chance to try again.\nCurious about the 
 Mediterranean diet\, the one that consistently ranks at the top of every 
 major list of the healthiest food diet options? Donna Liotto-Scocozza\, an 
 olive oil sommelier and purveyor of extra-virgin olive oils from around the 
 world\, will introduce you to the fine points of the Mediterranean way of 
 cooking and eating\, including a primer on the diet’s most essential 
 component\, extra-virgin olive oil. Donna will discuss the olive oil 
 basics\, including myths\, truths\, uses of olive oil and will have a 
 recipe handout. As part of the class\, she will offer a selection of EV 
 olive oils for tasting and purchasing.
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Conference Room\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School
