SUMMARY:Film Club - Online
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nDo you love movies? Do you wish you had others to discuss them 
 with after watching?  See assigned movies\, which may be on Netflix\, 
 Amazon Prime\, Hulu or on demand\, then join classmates to talk about 
 themes\, plot\, characters\, acting\, directing\, cinematography\, 
 costumes\, score\, trailers and/or viewer’s expectations.\n\nClass meets 
 Feb. 4\, 18\, Mar. 4\, 18\, Apr. 1\, 15\, 29\, May. 13\, 27\, and June 
 10..\n\nZoom Link will be sent weekly from Instructor. Students will view 
 one movie on their own for each class (sometimes a series may be assigned). 
 Instructor will email students one week before the first class.\n
