SUMMARY:Explore the Caribbean: A Crossroads of the World NEW - Online
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nBeyond the beautiful beaches and gentle breezes\, there are a 
 myriad of fascinating geographical and historical aspects to the Caribbean. 
 Join us as we delve into plate tectonics\, ocean currents\, climate\, the 
 history of indigenous groups\, European exploration\, piracy\, the 
 trans-Atlantic slave system\, and the introduction of sugar cane 
 cultivation in this fascinating part of the world.
LOCATION:Montclair - Offsite\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School, Lectures / History & Culture
