SUMMARY:CANCELLED - Experience George Washington in Art NEW
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nDeclared at his death “First in peace\, first in war\, and 
 first in the hearts of his countrymen\,” George Washington is revered 
 even today. Through works of art often drawn from area museums\, such as 
 the Metropolitan Museum of Art\, the Delaware Art Museum\, and the New York 
 Historical Society\, see how artists of his own time portrayed him for 
 posterity and how that posterity\, through its own crop of artists\, 
 commemorated his deeds.
