SUMMARY:Monthly Teen Volunteer Opportunity (Ages 12 - 18)
DESCRIPTION:Need some volunteer hours? Now's your chance! Every month\, 
 we'll have a different drop-in volunteer opportunity for all teens (12 - 18 
 year olds) in the Montclair area. Staff will be available to sign any forms 
 or documentation that you might have\, but it is your responsibility to 
 bring your paperwork.\n\nHere's the schedule:\n4 - 6pm on Wednesday\, 
 January 21 - Greeting Cards for Montclair Care Center\n4 - 6pm on 
 Wednesday\, February 11 - Greeting Cards for Sage Eldercare Meals on 
 Wheels\n4 - 6pm on Wednesday\, March 11 - ACTIVITY TBD\n4 - 6pm on 
