SUMMARY:Indoor Rowing
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to register on 
 the Adult School website.\n\nJoin the indoor rowing class\, get fit\, get 
 in shape and have fun all in one. Come and find out why Indoor rowing 
 (erging) is the most effective form of exercise that uses nearly every 
 muscle in your body. No experience is necessary\, rowing is easy to learn. 
 We will cater to all levels of fitness and proficiency\, focusing on 
 technique\, strength\, endurance\, core and more with varied\, music filled 
 workouts. Whatever your fitness goals\, erging will help you achieve 
 them.\n
