SUMMARY:The End of Power Transitions Among World Leaders NEW
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nFor the first time in centuries\, rising powers are not 
 replacing stagnant empires. Instead\, productivity is slowing\, populations 
 are shrinking and military conquest is growing harder. The world Is turning 
 into a club of aging incumbents\, circled by middle powers\, developing 
 countries and failing states.
LOCATION:Montclair Bellevue Ave Branch - First Floor\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
