SUMMARY:La Golondrina: Children's Musician & Author Sonia De Los Santos! (All ages welcome)
DESCRIPTION:On the porch of her grandmother's home\, a girl watches a 
 migratory swallow swoop and dart\, delighting in its song and imagining the 
 journey it will make–much like the one her papá is making\, and that she 
 will soon make too. Based on her popular song\, Latin Grammy nominee Sonia 
 De Los Santos's debut picture book is a joyful celebration of home\, 
 family\, and the journeys that shape our lives and communities. De Los 
 Santos reads La Golondrina\, followed by a performance of her song! Books 
 will be available for purchase and signing. Registration recommended for 
 updates and reminders.\n\n
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Auditorium\, Montclair Main - Cafe Area
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Library":MAILTO:events@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Author Talk, Children's Programs, Language, Music
