 101mins\n\nBeyond her historic role in the Montgomery Bus Boycott\, this 
 comprehensive dive into Civil Rights icon Rosa Parks sheds light on her 
 extensive organizing\, radical politics\, and lifelong dedication to 
 activism. Watch the trailer here.\n\n\nSeating for the film is first come\, 
 first served. No registration is required.
